        "solutionCode": "_inputs = []\nvalue = _parse_arg(_inputs[0]) if len(_inputs) > 0 else \"\"\n\nvalues = [0, '', None, 'Hello', 5]\nfor value in values:\n    if value:\n        print(f'{value} is Truthy')\n    else:\n        print(f'{value} is Falsy')"
